last_episode_to_air.name: A Father's Secret
last_episode_to_air.overview: When the body of William Sparkman is found hanging from a tree with his arms bound and FED scrawled on his chest, Kentucky State Police and the FBI must unravel a complicated mystery.

name: Accident, Suicide or Murder
overview: Exploring the unbelievable true stories of suspicious deaths by retracing the investigation from start to finish, dissecting the red flags and undeniable evidence, and strange behavior that put the tragedy in question.

episodes.name: The Sinister Minister
episodes.overview: The beloved wife of a respected pastor dies in a tragic car accident. The community mourns until a congregant commits suicide, triggering an investigation that brings deadly secrets to light.

episodes.name: Blood and Justice
episodes.overview: The justice system in Texas is turned upside down when a family suspects foul play despite authorities' claims that the wife of a former cop committed suicide.

episodes.name: Blood Betrayal
episodes.overview: Despite what authorities claim, a family doubts a young father would have committed suicide, and it's up to a dedicated police chief to help a mother and daughter unravel the mystery surrounding his suspicious death.

episodes.name: Two Deaths, One Suspect
episodes.overview: A grieving husband claims his wife accidentally fell to her death. Investigators become suspicious after learning his first wife also died in a freak accident.

episodes.name: Killer Detective
episodes.overview: When a Texas police detective finds his wife dead from a gunshot wound his fellow detectives work to uncover if her death was an accident, a suicide, or something more sinister.

episodes.name: Killer Crash
episodes.overview: A man is left injured in an accident off a mountain road that killed his wife, but a family is suspicious of the crash and intend to uncover the real story.

episodes.name: Deadly Prophecy
episodes.overview: A young pastor grieves after his wife dies in a house fire. But when shocking secrets are revealed, a community is shattered. Could a prophecy have predicted her death?

episodes.name: Finger on the Trigger
episodes.overview: A frantic woman calls 9-1-1 saying her boyfriend shot himself. But when the story keeps changing, it takes a risky gambit to unravel the truth.

episodes.name: Investigated by Paul Holes: What Happened to Morgan Ingram?
episodes.overview: Paul Holes re-examines the suspicious death of Morgan Ingram. Her parents claim she was stalked and eventually murdered, but law enforcement closed her case as a suicide by overdose. What really happened to this beloved 20 year old?

episodes.name: Behind the Locked Door
episodes.overview: A beautiful young woman is found in her locked apartment with 20-stab wounds. The Medical Examiner classifies her death as murder. But when the M.E. later changes the ruling to suicide, the decision forces her family into the fight of their lives.

episodes.name: Killer Fetish
episodes.overview: First responders are called to the fatal shooting of a 28-year-old woman; while her estranged husband claims their bizarre sex game ended in suicide, investigators and the victim’s family believe the case to be a cold-blooded murder.

episodes.name: Twin Tragedy
episodes.overview: Identical twin sisters are involved in a horrific crash on the island of Maui. Miraculously, one sister survives after their car plunges over the side of a cliff. Was this a tragic accident or something more ominous?

episodes.name: The Missing Bullet
episodes.overview: A man discovers the body of his fiancé with an apparent self-inflicted gunshot wound. Her death is ruled a suicide but authorities are puzzled when they can’t find the fatal bullet. The discovery of the missing bullet turns the case upside down.

episodes.name: A Shot in the Dark
episodes.overview: A young woman is found with a fatal head wound and her hand on the shotgun. Her fiancé claims she killed herself but grieving family members insist the suicide scene was staged. The case goes cold until a new prosecutor takes a second look.

episodes.name: Red Sash Death
episodes.overview: A beloved grandmother is found with a red bathrobe sash knotted around her neck. Her death looks like suicide until the Medical Examiner rules homicide. The victim’s 76-year-old husband is charged with murder but the case takes a surprising turn.

episodes.name: Deadly Crash
episodes.overview: A car crash on a rural highway leaves one woman dead while her husband walks away unscathed. It appears to be a tragic accident. Still, one state trooper can’t shake the feeling the crash is anything but routine.

episodes.name: In The Fire
episodes.overview: Firefighters discover the charred remains of a young wife and mother but the flames didn’t kill her. She sustained a gunshot wound to the head and the evidence points to suicide. Loved ones argue it’s a case of murder.

episodes.name: The Cop's Wife
episodes.overview: A police officer discovers his young wife with a fatal gunshot wound from his service weapon and her death is ruled a suicide; investigators uncover a shocking story.

episodes.name: Dead in The Water
episodes.overview: A husband discovers his wife face down in their bathtub; her death appears to be an accident, but questions are raised about how she drowned.

episodes.name: Young Deadly Love
episodes.overview: A young man calls 911 to report his fiancé fatally shot herself in their bed. Her family insists she would never take her own life. The investigation drags on for years until an unexpected development leads to a stunning conclusion.

episodes.name: Death In A Small Town
episodes.overview: An 80-year-old woman is found in her home lying in a pool of blood. Her death is ruled an accident, but her family suspects foul play. In a tight-knit community where neighbors look out for each other, who would want to hurt a beloved grandmother?

episodes.name: Deadly Betrayal
episodes.overview: A decorated war hero is found in his home, the victim of an apparent drug overdose. Investigators uncover a twisted story of fraud and betrayal that leads to a stunning conclusion.

episodes.name: Dark Echoes
episodes.overview: A weekend trip to an Alaskan lodge turns deadly for a young mother when she's shot and killed by her boyfriend. The death is ruled an accident and the case is closed until an eerily similar incident in Montana drives investigators to reopen the case.

episodes.name: Unholy Secrets
episodes.overview: A pastor places a frantic call and pleads for help to save his fiancée, who, he says, just shot herself, but as investigators look closer at the crime scene, a darker side to this happy relationship stuns everyone.

episodes.name: Lover's Chair
episodes.overview: Investigators uncover a web of lies a decade after a couple's romantic evening atop Rockefeller Lookout in New Jersey ends with the wife's tragic death.

episodes.name: Relentless
episodes.overview: A Texas woman's apparent suicide devastates the family that she leaves behind, but after one investigator dedicates decades to solving the mystery of what drove her to make such a tragic decision, a far more sinister truth is discovered.

episodes.name: A Deadly Inferno
episodes.overview: Tragedy strikes a rural Nebraska town when their beloved high school volleyball coach dies in a fiery car accident. But as investigators reconstruct her tragic death, the resulting clues steer the investigation to reveal a horrifying series of events.

episodes.name: Vanished With The Tides
episodes.overview: An apparent victim of an accidental drowning washes ashore on idyllic Cocoa Beach, FL, but as investigators pull back the layers of the victim's personal life, a far murkier truth is revealed.

episodes.name: A Deadly Dose
episodes.overview: In the early morning hours after Valentine's Day, a man is found dead after an apparent drug overdose, but a jail informant gives investigators a tip that abruptly changes the case, and a deadly pattern of deaths in the family is revealed.

episodes.name: Thicker Than Water
episodes.overview: An elderly woman is found dead in her home outside of Boston after an apparent accidental fall down her stairs, but with the help of a confidential informant, police obtain shocking audio that reveals the truth behind her death.

episodes.name: Execution Enigma
episodes.overview: Investigators suspect foul play when they discover a body lying along a lonely stretch of New Mexico highway, but the bizarre trail of evidence only deepens the dark enigma surrounding a seemingly well-respected family man.

episodes.name: The Pact
episodes.overview: In May 2017, a teenage girl dies from an apparent suicide. Utah investigators suspect that there's more to the scene than meets the eye, and a close friend may have helped her end her own life. As evidence comes to light, a darker truth is revealed.

episodes.name: Relentless Pursuit
episodes.overview: Investigators in a rural mountain community are baffled by the accidental shooting of a young mother. But her determined daughter's decades-long quest fractures the so-called facts to reveal a darker story hidden beneath.

episodes.name: Out of Thin Air
episodes.overview: When a body is discovered in an upscale Boston suburb all signs point to homicide. But the clues in this unique case send investigators on a journey to discover an unbelievable truth that seems more like the plot of a movie.

episodes.name: In Sickness and in Wealth
episodes.overview: When a once prominent heart surgeon is found dead in his bed after suffering mysterious health conditions, detectives must determine if it's natural causes or a nefarious money grab.

episodes.name: Fallen
episodes.overview: A beautiful scenic drive up the coast of California turns deadly when a young woman falls from an overlook in Big Sur. But when the people closest to her hear about the tragic accident, they're convinced that something more nefarious is going on.

episodes.name: A Perfectly Designed Staircase
episodes.overview: When a woman is found dead at the bottom of her staircase, Investigators focus on her husband as the main suspect. But family and friends rally behind him, pitting the reputation of a gentle spouse against the spectre of a bizarre double-life.

episodes.name: Blown Away
episodes.overview: When a successful family man is discovered in the rubble of a deadly explosion, investigators desperately try to determine if it was a planned hit, an attempted terrorist attack, or something else...

episodes.name: Blood on the Tracks
episodes.overview: A young woman who is lying on railroad tracks is hit by a freight train, but when her cause of death comes into question, investigators push to reopen the case; after years of dedicated police work, the buried truth finally comes to light.

episodes.name: Between a Cop and a Hard Place
episodes.overview: A police officer reports that he found his wife dead in their home. The scene says suicide, the family says otherwise, and an epic investigation spills across state lines to reveal the truth.

episodes.name: Death of a Salesman
episodes.overview: A local celebrity is fatally shot in his bedroom. Although debt and depression point to suicide, forensic evidence and expert testimony hint at something more sinister. The truth revealed will draw a line between a grieving spouse and a black widow.

episodes.name: Dark Prophecy
episodes.overview: A 2004 welfare check spirals into a sinister tableau of death when Idaho Sheriffs make forceful entry into a home only to discover a horrific crime scene provoked by a cult-like prophecy, revealing a shocking truth that no one saw coming.

episodes.name: The Big Shot
episodes.overview: When a late-night party in the home of a celebrity basketball player turns deadly, a curious web of lies leads detectives on a rocky road to the truth to find justice for the unlikely victim.

episodes.name: Father Knows Death
episodes.overview: Two unusual accidents that are two decades apart leave a family suspicious of a father who appears to benefit from tragedy.

episodes.name: The Hunter and the Hunted
episodes.overview: A young immigrant mother is killed in a hunting accident while out with her fiancé. As police investigate, they unravel a tangle of romantic relationships, money and motives to reveal the terrifying truth of what really happened.

episodes.name: A Family Fight
episodes.overview: Found with a gunshot wound to her chest, a woman’s family seeks justice for 20 years after the would-be murder suspect proclaims suicide.

episodes.name: Playing With Fire
episodes.overview: Investigators following clues in a viral Tik-Tok trend begin to realize that nothing is as it seems after two bodies are discovered in the ashes of a suspicious house fire.

episodes.name: California Crash
episodes.overview: Detectives are led down a winding path involving an alleged government conspiracy and a citywide manhunt after a tragic car accident leaves a mother dead and her daughter in critical condition.

episodes.name: Hollywood Horror
episodes.overview: Detectives chase the truth when a struggling Hollywood actress and a famed music producer engage in a late-night rendezvous that takes a deadly turn.

episodes.name: Beauty and the Politician
episodes.overview: A married politician's day with his mistress comes to a tragic end when she's shot to death in her driveway. Was this murder in a possessive fit of rage or had his refusal to leave his wife finally pushed her over the edge to commit suicide?

episodes.name: Mystery in Montebello
episodes.overview: When a 41-year-old math teacher suddenly dies at home without an official cause of death, investigators find his new wife holds the clues.

episodes.name: Drowning in Lies
episodes.overview: When a famed musician's ex-wife drowns in her new boyfriend's pool, her famous family fights for justice. Was this a drunken accidental drowning or did he do her in?

episodes.name: Friend or Foe?
episodes.overview: Two young friends who are prominent in the online deaf community pursue a shared dream in the northern California wilderness; when the pact turns sour and one of them goes missing, detectives must make sense of their perilous and deadly journey.

episodes.name: Shattered Glass
episodes.overview: When a beloved wife and doting husband are involved in a bizarre car accident, only one of them survives; as inconsistencies pile up, detectives are left questioning if this really was a freak accident or a clever attempt to hide a murder.

episodes.name: Drop By Drop
episodes.overview: When first responders find a self-made millionaire dead in his lakeside mansion, initial signs point to a natural cause of death. As investigators probe further, however, they uncover a toxicological bombshell that blows the case wide open.

episodes.name: A Mysterious Overdose
episodes.overview: A troubled Las Vegas lawyer goes to sleep early while her psychologist husband takes their daughters out to dinner. When she doesn't wake up the next morning, her family is convinced there's more to this incident than investigators initially believe.

episodes.name: A Loaded Crime Scene
episodes.overview: A husband shoots his wife across the kitchen table while cleaning a gun; he claims it was an accident, but when her colleague mysteriously dies a few days later, investigators take a closer look at the case.

episodes.name: Secrets in the Scrapyard
episodes.overview: When a young mother is found dead at work from an apparent suicide, her church community is shocked by the loss; however, revelations of torrid infidelity and rampant drug use lead investigators on a decade-long search for the truth behind her death.

episodes.name: Death in Shallow Waters
episodes.overview: A husband comes home to find his wife dead next to their outdoor fish pond. Her cause of death appears to be from a trip and fall, but when investigators follow a twisted trail of familial deceit and greed, new truths bring her death into question.

episodes.name: A Doctor's Care
episodes.overview: After a former beauty queen and mother of eight is found unconscious in her bathtub following a facelift, her death appears to be an accident. When her doctor husband is caught in a series of deceptions, it raises alarms with investigators.

episodes.name: Cutting Ties
episodes.overview: On the edge of divorce, a couple's argument over custody turns deadly; the husband claims he killed his wife in self-defense when she attacked him with scissors, but a look into his past holds a deadly secret.

episodes.name: Fiery Grave
episodes.overview: When a young husband dies in a fiery car crash, investigators believe his death was a tragic accident, but when his widow seems more relieved than aggrieved, detectives make a shocking discovery.

episodes.name: Troubled Water
episodes.overview: When a housewife dies in her hot tub, detectives in a normally quiet Idaho town first believe it to be a horrible accident. But the investigation leads back to the unsolved murder of her husband, reminding police that lightning never strikes twice.

episodes.name: In Her Words
episodes.overview: When a pregnant army wife and mother are found shot to death in her home, it is ruled a suicide, but dogged police work unlocks a devious plot and secrets buried in ashes thousands of miles away.

episodes.name: Revenge on the Road
episodes.overview: A former Gang Unit investigator is found dead in his crashed van on the freeway and all signs point to a DUI.

episodes.name: Justice for Jennifer?
episodes.overview: Jennifer, a well-liked college student was found dead under suspicious circumstances. The case dragged on for years as the findings of police investigators and medical examiners seemed to conflict with each other and with the testimonies of those who knew her.

episodes.name: Among Us
episodes.overview: When a group of hospital patients dies of natural causes, authorities become alarmed. It takes more than 20 years and a dedicated investigation team to convict a murderer.

episodes.name: Dark Plunge
episodes.overview: A couple's pickup is found submerged in a lake, and the wife's death appears to be the result of a horrible accident until investigators learn that not everything is as it seems in this pair's union.

guest_stars.character: Self - Police Reporter, New York Post
guest_stars.name: Larry Celona

episodes.name: Let Us Prey
episodes.overview: A man is found in a west Los Angeles alley, dead from an apparent hit and run; when investigators dig deeper, strange suspects emerge in a twisted tale of greed.

guest_stars.character: Self - L.A. Crime Historian & True Crime Author
guest_stars.name: Joan Renner

episodes.name: Ashes to Ashes
episodes.overview: When a man is found burned to death in his home workshop, his wife is charged with murder; the ensuing arson investigation points in a very different direction.

episodes.name: Washed Away
episodes.overview: A deadly fall in the shower claims the life of beloved community leader Leslie Neulander in Dewitt, NY, but when a friend and former medical examiner voices her suspicions, the case takes a shocking turn.

episodes.name: A Father's Secret
episodes.overview: When the body of William Sparkman is found hanging from a tree with his arms bound and FED scrawled on his chest, Kentucky State Police and the FBI must unravel a complicated mystery.
